metadata.name: Katie Rogers - Confidence Outfit
metadata.description:
From DESPOP PUBLISHING IP- THE INFAMOUS KATIE ROGERS
Purchase of this piece includes an exclusive signed print

Katie Rogers is a  British publicist working in the cutthroat world of Hollywood, trying to save the careers of her estranged clients whilst juggling her everyday life. Created in 2004, Katie has appeared in books, hosted parties, and was even optioned as a TV series.  Her motion comic book THE TROUBLE WITH KATIE ROGERS premiered on the Madefire Motion book App at SDCC 2016.  A brand new Graphic Novel is in the works.
